{"tid":1847542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[快d入黎答我] 二百萬人遊行 點解得7萬5人入咗三罷channel","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:41:13.000Z","uid":150065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbaa8669f3a20aef68023eaef8af4dea394d9ab","tid":1847542,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"支那肺炎殺到埋身，政府冇做過野咁滯，一直唔肯封關，仲要比大陸人免費來港醫病。由得支那些人一車車咁落黎，再係咁落去社區爆發係遲早嘅事，封關實在迫在眉睫。<br />\n<br />\n三罷channel 其實都宣傳咗好耐，擺過街站，亦都上過好多次熱門叫人join。但直到宜家呢個moment，竟然得7萬5人入咗呢個channel。再對比其他熱門d嘅channel有成20萬人join，真係好難唔嬲點解香港人唔識保障自己嘅利益，唔識反抗，任由自己比政府同資方剝削。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTwwymN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTwwymN.png&h=900f9dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wgDXOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wgDXOt.png&h=60d41932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDYZHe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDYZHe9.png&h=0103b407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生死關頭，醫護話要罷工，大家口講支持醫護罷工，但連三罷channel 都冇入到。香港人到底係咪鍾意翻工鍾意到連命仔都唔要? 成日話唔翻工冇錢開飯會死，咁有冇諗過幾乎每間公司都有大陸人嗰陣，宜家再翻工你會感染肺炎而死? 唔翻工你最多會冇咗份工，繼續翻工你分分鐘冇咗條命。當中黃藍都可以一齊set rb 嗰陣，點解香港人唔可以一齊罷工? <br />\n<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=6ba0ac97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️Group List⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/1040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F1040&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=623b6c59\" data-auto-link target=